ta-villalar-comuneros/59795.html Castilla y Le\u00f3n se viste de fiesta en Villalar de los Comuneros] Lagacetadesalamanca.es, 30 April 2012 {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n|-\n|2013||20,000<ref>[http://kioskoymas.abc.es/noticias/comunidad-castillaleon/20130424/abcp-nostalgia-manifiesto-villalar-20130424.html Sin nostalgia del Manifiesto de Villalar] [[ABC (newspaper)|ABC]], 24 April 2013 {{in lang|es}}</ref>||20,000<ref>[http://www.teinteresa.es/politica/personas-Dia-Castilla-Leon-Villalar_0_906510761.html M\u00e1s de 20.000 personas viven el D\u00eda de Castilla y Le\u00f3n en Villalar] Teinteresa.es, 23 April 2013 {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n|-\n|colspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"|<small>Unless otherwise noted, compiled from<br> Source: [[#refP\u00e9rezyP\u00e9rez|P\u00e9rez y P\u00e9rez (2005)]], p.&nbsp;317</small>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n* This article incorporates text translated from the [[Spanish Wikipedia]] article [[:es:D\u00eda de Castilla y Le\u00f3n|''D\u00eda de Castilla y Le\u00f3n'']], licensed under the {{srlink|Wikipedia:Text of the GNU Free Documentation License|GFDL}}.\n*<cite id=\"#refP\u00e9rezyP\u00e9rez\">P\u00e9rez y P\u00e9rez, Federico (2005). ''Castilla y Le\u00f3n: Autonom\u00eda dividida. De la Guerra de las Comunidades a la campa de Villalar de los Comuneros (1520\u20132004)''. Burgos: Dossoles. {{ISBN|84-87528-92-9}}</cite>\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070831024417/http://www.boe.es/g/es/bases_datos/doc.php?coleccion=iberlex&id=1986%2F90009&codmap= Text of the Law establishing the holiday] {{in lang|es}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Castile And Leon Day}}\n[[Category:Public holidays in Spain]]\n[[Category:Castilian culture]]\n[[Category:April observances]]\n[[Category:National holidays]]\n[[Category:Spring (season) events in Spain]]\n", "name_user": "46.9.203.65", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Castile_and_Le%C3%B3n_Day"}
